00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:06.840
I went to every single day and every single&nbsp;
moment of the court case. This was the first&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:14.960
time I actually witnessed right in front of me&nbsp;
state intention to lie, to deceive, to gaslight...&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:22.162
The embedded misogyny, the homophobia, the&nbsp;
transphobia, the arrogance of the police...

00:00:22.162 --> 00:00:27.600
Again, because of the tone of the way the police had 
been&nbsp;talking about these things... Very much felt like,

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:34.160
kind of, a moral panic of, “They’ve got to close&nbsp;
down these sex rooms in case someone unknowingly&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:39.440
wandered in,” which was impossible. It was&nbsp;
made very clear that this was a sexual space,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:43.240
and that there was going to be naked people&nbsp;
and there was going to be sexual activity, and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:43.240 --> 00:00:45.849
you could not walk in there 
and be surprised by&nbsp;that.

