00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:10.760
really fortunate that I was in my late twenties&nbsp;
before I felt that knowledge, that I was part&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:10.760 --> 00:02:16.480
of a community that I could not absolutely count&nbsp;
